                "category": "offensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>A creature damaged by the godclaw hellcrown's spectral lash Strike must attempt a @Check[fortitude|dc:23] save. On a failure, the tip of the lash is embedded in the creature, dealing @Damage[1d6[persistent,bleed]] damage and imparting a –5-foot status penalty to the target's Speeds for 1 minute. Each additional embedded tip increases the bleed damage by 1 and the penalty to Speed by 5 feet. A creature can remove a tip with an Interact action to reduce the amount of bleed damage and the penalty to Speed. Pulling out the last tip removes both conditions.</p>"
                },
