                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>All creatures that can see the hellcrown and are affected by agony lash must attempt a @Check[will|dc:25] saving throw. A creature that fails is @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Frightened]{Frightened 1}, and on a critical failure, it becomes @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Fleeing] for as long as it's frightened. Regardless of the result, the creature is then temporarily immune to Forbidding Stare for 10 minutes.</p>"
